title: Md. changes name, structure of economic development agency
text: Maryland officials promoted on Thursday a restructuring of the state's economic development arm, saying the newly named Department of Commerce will foster a more business-friendly culture. The agency had been known as the Department of Business and Economic Development since the Glendening administration.... ...
